Gratitude be, for being on the verge of the most important turning point of the century. The fourth industrial revolution with its rewards and punishments, promises change, and a test for the best of us. As the world enters a new era, nothing is truly ever lost, and preparation shall finally meet opportunity.

The uncertain tomorrow will not be a reason for an idle today. Technology, indistinguishable from magic, is here, and never was time kinder than now, to make impact as an individual component in the greater human machine.

A pursuit of dreams fueled by a chronology of experiences and skills, reaches convergence under the shadow of information technology, data, dev-ops, and business analysis, in order to contribute towards something larger than life.
